  "time_ut": 1656609322,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u2019\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0ba4\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "'Ready to take over government in short term'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "We are ready to take over the government for a short period of time. Anurakumara Dissanayake, President of National People's Shakti, has said that we will resolve the basic issues in a short period of time, hold elections, form a stable government and develop plans to boost the economy in a few years.",
        "The country is completely paralyzed due to wrong decisions of the government. All the destruction a country can face has been caused simultaneously by politics tied to the economic policy pursued by the existing governments.",
        "What decisions did the government take to save the country from this devastation? They said Ranil Wickremesinghe had international connections and could bring in dollars because he knew whites. But when Ranil came to power, he saved the Rajapaksas.",
        "People's problems are not solved. People had to wait in queues for days, agriculture was destroyed as a gang of crooks looted public property. Therefore, steps should be taken to recover looted public property and arrest them. This cannot be done by simply overthrowing the government.",
        "He said people should take to the streets with the aim of punishing the corrupt and corrupt people who have wreaked havoc in this country and recovering the looted property."
      ],
